{"lemma":"سَوْرَةٌ","slug":"سَوْرَةٌ","root":"س.#.ر","root_slug":"س-_-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/س-_-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"سَوْرَةٌ","root":"سور","pos":"N","occurrence_count":10},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n21209"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8E%D9%88%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sura, surah","examples":[{"text":"Holonym: اَلْقُرْآن (al-qurʔān)"},{"text":"Meronym: آيَة (ʔāya)"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"severity, vehemence, sharpness"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Assigned to the root س و ر (s w r). It is not clear from which word it was borrowed, it might be from Classical Syriac ܫܘܽܪܳܐ (šūrā, “wall; also figuratively for any divider”), compare سُور (sūr, “wall”) from the same word, or from Classical Syriac ܣܽܘܪܓܳܕܳܐ (sūrgāḏā, “line; writing”), or from Hebrew סִדְרָה (siḏrā, “technical term for the section marks in the Hebrew scriptures”), or from Hebrew שִׁיר (šīr, “lyric song; poem”), or from a variant vocalization of Classical Syriac ܣܻܝܪܳܐ (sīrā, “thread; chapter, topical division of a book”)."},"ipa":["/suː.ra/","/saw.ra/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n21209","headword_ar":"سَوْرَةٌ","root":"swr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A leap,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spring."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"assault"},{"kind":"text","text":"of wine"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon the head;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or its"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rush into the head:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in like manner, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"assault,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rush,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of venom, such as that of the scorpion: (S:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"force,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strength,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of wine &c.; (M, K, Msb, and MF voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Had~N","text_ar":"حَدٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":";) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suwaArN","text_ar":"سُوَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, K;) and in like manner, of hunger: (Msb:) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overpowering influence"},{"kind":"text","text":"of wine"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon the head:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suwaArN","text_ar":"سُوَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"creeping"},{"kind":"text","text":"of wine"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the head:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saworapN","text_ar":"سَوْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said to signify the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"assault,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"force,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intoxicating operation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overpowering influence upon the head,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Humay~aA","text_ar":"حُمَيَّا"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"produced by the creeping"},{"kind":"text","text":"of wine,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"through, the drinker:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in like manner,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraHK","text_ar":"فَرَحٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suwaAru","text_ar":"سُوَارُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a motion of joy like the creeping of wine in the head."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  [(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A paroxysm of fever."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b4-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An ebullition, a fierceness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an impetuousness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anger; as when] one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a ligaDabihi lasaworapF","text_ar":"اـِنَّ لِغَضَبِهِ لَسَوْرَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily his anger has an ebullition, a fierceness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an impetuousness"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:) [(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an outburst,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"outbreak,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anger: and] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anger"},{"kind":"text","text":"itself: [or (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1465},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fit of anger,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"irritation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saworaAtN","text_ar":"سَوْرَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) ―         -b5-  [(assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flush,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"impetuosity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of youth: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Humay~aA","text_ar":"حُمَيَّا"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Impetuousness"},{"kind":"text","text":"in war. (A.) [It is said in the TA that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN *uwsaworapK fiY AlHarobi","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ ذُوسَوْرَةٍ فِى الحَرْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw naZarK $adiydK","text_ar":"ذُو نَظَرٍ شَدِيدٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one has strong inspection in war:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but I think that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naZarK","text_ar":"نَظَرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is here a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saTowK","text_ar":"سَطْوٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"impetuousness."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Violence, force,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"oppression, and tyranny,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a Sultán: (S, K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"might,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"valour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA,) of a Sultán. (TA.) ―         -b8-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Vehemence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intenseness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of cold: (K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehement,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intense, cold."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*atohu Als~aworapu","text_ar":"اَخَذَتْهُ السَّوْرَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Intense cold seized him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b9-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suwrapN","text_ar":"سُورَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}